{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"禁止修改的标头","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Forbidden_header_name","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>禁止修改的标头</strong>指的是不能在代码中通过编程的方式进行修改的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers\">HTTP 标头</a>，具体指 HTTP <strong>请求</strong>标头（和<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Forbidden_response_header_name\">禁止修改的响应标头</a>形成对比）。</p>\n<p>因为用户代理保留对此类标头的完全控制，所以它们被禁止修改。保留以 <code>Sec-</code> 开头的名称，以用于在使用 <a href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-fetch\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">fetch 算法</a>的请求中创建安全的新标头，这些 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/API\">API</a> 授予开发人员对标头的控制权，例如：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a>。</p>\n<p>禁止修改的标头包括以 <code>Proxy-</code> 和 <code>Sec-</code> 开头的标头，以及下面列出的标头：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Accept-Charset\"><code>Accept-Charset</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Accept-Encoding\"><code>Accept-Encoding</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Request-Headers\"><code>Access-Control-Request-Headers</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Access-Control-Request-Method\"><code>Access-Control-Request-Method</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Connection\"><code>Connection</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Length\"><code>Content-Length</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Cookie\"><code>Cookie</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Date\"><code>Date</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/DNT\"><code>DNT</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Expect\"><code>Expect</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Feature-Policy\"><code>Feature-Policy</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Host\"><code>Host</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Keep-Alive\"><code>Keep-Alive</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Origin\"><code>Origin</code></a></li>\n  <li><code>Proxy-</code></li>\n  <li><code>Sec-</code></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Referer\"><code>Referer</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/TE\"><code>TE</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Trailer\"><code>Trailer</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Transfer-Encoding\"><code>Transfer-Encoding</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Upgrade\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Upgrade (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Via\"><code>Via</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> <a href=\"https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#terminology-headers\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">根据规范</a>中的禁止修改的标头列表（Firefox 43 中实现了它），<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/User-Agent\"><code>User-Agent</code></a> 标头不再被禁止，现在可以设置在 Fetch 的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Headers\">Headers</a> 对象中，或者通过 <code>XMLHttpRequest</code> 的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/setRequestHeader\">setRequestHeader()</a> 方法设置。但是，Chrome 会不做提示地从 Fetch 请求中丢弃这个标头（请参阅 <a href=\"https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=571722\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Chromium bug 571722</a>）。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Forbidden_response_header_name\">禁止修改的响应标头</a>（术语表）</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"禁止修改的标头指的是不能在代码中通过编程的方式进行修改的 HTTP 标头，具体指 HTTP 请求标头（和禁止修改的响应标头形成对比）。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Forbidden header name","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Nombre de encabezado prohibido","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Nom d'en-tête interdit","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Forbidden header name (禁止ヘッダー名)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Nome de cabeçalho proibido","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Запрещённое имя заголовка","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/forbidden_header_name","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/forbidden_header_name/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Forbidden_header_name","title":"禁止修改的标头"}],"pageTitle":"禁止修改的标头 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}